# Wiki Maintenance

- Prefer maintaining durable notes over leaving knowledge in chat history.
- For important new sources: register source, create or update a source note, update the relevant area or synthesis note, and capture the change in the log if needed.
- Keep starter notes generic and reusable in the public template.
- Use synthesis notes when a topic starts to shape decisions across multiple notes.
- Do not create ceremony-only notes or over-fragment the wiki.
